\c 40
\s Josefa anodudzira hope
\p
\v 1 Zvino zvakaitika shure kwezvinhu izvi, \add kuti\add* mudiri wamambo weEgipita nemubiki vakatadzira tenzi wavo, mambo weEgipita.
\v 2 Zvino Farao wakatsamwira vatenwa vake vaviri, ivo mukuru wavadiri nomukuru wavabiki.
\v 3 Zvino wakavakumikidza muchitokisi, mumba memukuru wevarindi, mutirongo, nzvimbo makange makasungwa Josefa.
\v 4 Mukuru wavarindi ndokuraira Josefa kuva navo, iye akavashandira, uye vakava nenguva muchitokisi.
\p
\v 5 Zvino vose vaviri vakarota hope, umwe neumwe hope dzake, usiku humwe, umwe neumwe maererano nedudziro yehope dzake, mudiri nemubiki vamambo weEgipita vakange vakasungwa mutirongo.
\v 6 Zvino Josefa wakapinda kwavari mangwanani, ndokuvatarira, ndokuona, zvino tarira, vakasuruvara.
\v 7 Zvino wakabvunza vatenwa vaFarao vakange vachengetwa pamwe naye mumba matenzi wake, achiti: Sei zviso zvenyu zvakasuruvara nhasi?
\v 8 Zvino vakati kwaari: Tarota hope, zvino hakuna mududziri wadzo. Josefa ndokuti kwavari: Dudziro hadzisi dzaMwari here? Dondirondedzerai henyu.
\v 9 Zvino mukuru wevadiri wakarondedzera hope dzake kuna Josefa, ndokuti kwaari: Muhope dzangu, zvino tarira, muzambiringa pamberi pangu;
\v 10 uye pamuzambiringa paiva nematavi matatu; uye aiita seanotunga, ndokubudisa maruva; uye masumbu awo akabereka mazambiringa akaibva.
\v 11 Zvino mukombe waFarao wakange uri muruoko rwangu; ini ndokutora mazambiringa, ndikaasvinira mumukombe waFarao, ndikaisa mukombe muruoko rwaFarao.
\p
\v 12 Josefa akati kwaari, Kududzirwa kwadzo ndiko: Matavi matatu mazuva matatu;
\v 13 mazuva matatu agere kupera Farao achasimudza musoro wako, nokukudzosera kubasa rako; ipapo uchaisa mukombe waFarao muruoko rwakezve, sezvawaiita kare uchiri mudiri wake.
\p
\v 14 Asi undirangarire hako kana woitirwa zvakanaka; undiitire tsitsi, undireverere kuna Farao, kuti ndibudiswe paimba ino;
\p
\v 15 Nokuti zvirokwazvo, ndakabiwa kunyika yavaHebheru; napano handina kuita chinhu chakafanira kuti vandiise mugomba iri.
\p
\v 16 Zvino mukuru wavabiki akati aona kuti dudziro yakanaka, akati kuna Josefa, Neniwo ndakange ndiri pakurota kwangu, ndikaona tswanda nhatu dzechingwa chichena dzakange dziri pamusoro wangu;
\v 17 mutswanda yapamusoro makange mune zvokudya zvamarudzi ose zvakabikwa zvaFarao; shiri dzikazvidya mutswanda yaiva pamusoro wangu.
\p
\v 18 Ipapo Josefa akapindura, akati, Kududzirwa kwadzo ndiko: Tswanda nhatu mazuva matatu;
\v 19 mazuva matatu agere kupera, Farao achasimudza musoro wako akaubvisa pamusoro pako, akusungirire pamuti; shiri dzichadya nyama yako dzichiibvisa kwauri.
\p
\v 20 Zvino nomusi wetatu, musi wokuzvarwa kwaFarao, iye akaitira varanda vake vose mutambo. Akasimudza musoro womukuru wavadiri, nomusoro womukuru wavabiki pakati pavaranda vake,
\v 21 akadzosera mukuru wavadiri kubasa rake rokudira kwake, akapa mukombe waFarao muruoko rwaFarao;
\v 22 asi akasungirira mukuru wavabiki sezvavakange vadudzirwa naJosefa.
\v 23 Asi mukuru wavadiri haana kurangarira Josefa, asi akamukanganwa.
